Cell["\<\
All topologies with at least one accepted interior or boundary HR stratum. \
The internal labels x0,x1,... are the Feynman parameters in the scaling \
vectors; external leg p_i emerges from vertex i.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"6c2ed36c-a8aa-40ef-af6f-0aa9a0e7b6d5"],

